    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进一个俄罗斯人的忧郁世界，生活在典型的后苏联赫鲁晓夫的荒凉环境中。你的生活在沉迷、平凡的工作和无尽的自省中循环往复，背景是一个被时间遗忘的外省小镇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793150/extras/6a4ebc70b270d351a8aecddd6c340d0d.poster.avif?t=1766067530\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793150/extras/6a4ebc70b270d351a8aecddd6c340d0d.webm?t=1766067530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793150/extras/6a4ebc70b270d351a8aecddd6c340d0d.mp4?t=1766067530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以感受到原始、粗粝但又十分怀旧的氛围。漫无目的地在小区里闲逛，穿过车库，探索空旷的操场，或者坐在堆满烟头的花坛边抽烟。当外部世界的重压压得你喘不过气来的时候，就退回到你的小公寓里。看看你过去的纪念品，上上网，抚摸你忠实的老鼠，或者沉浸在与你心灵相通的老电视节目和广告中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793150/extras/dbff9a8a062c1a52e06aa43eca39da50.poster.avif?t=1766067530\" width=628 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793150/extras/dbff9a8a062c1a52e06aa43eca39da50.webm?t=1766067530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793150/extras/dbff9a8a062c1a52e06aa43eca39da50.mp4?t=1766067530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，你不是在追逐宏大的冒险。相反，你要探索的是生活中安静、平淡的角落--抽根烟、在荒凉的院子里散步，或者仅仅是拥抱这一切的甜蜜冷漠。这是你怀旧的乐园，有些行为会带来意想不到的后果，你要做的就是尝试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥抱漫不经心的生活，在熟悉而空虚的生活中度过灰暗的日子。</p>",
